15
00:00:55,279 --> 00:00:56,691
- Disseste.
- E?

16
00:00:56,936 --> 00:00:57,881
Não arranjei.

17
00:00:59,329 --> 00:01:00,433
Vamos.

18
00:01:01,974 --> 00:01:03,116
Boa noite, Sheldon.

19
00:01:03,117 --> 00:01:04,890
